<html>
  <head>
    <title>Gazelle OAuth 2.0 Demo</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </head>
<body>
  <div class="container p-5">
    <p>
      Welcome to a demonstration of acquiring a Gazelle OAuth 2.0 token and using it to query the Gazelle API as described
      in the <a href="https://gazelleapp.io/docs/graphql/private/authentication" target="_blank">Gazelle authorization and authentication documentation</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="<%= @authorize_url %>">Click here</a> to authorize this demo app to your Gazelle account.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
